            "id": "s_l4_3",
            "type": "code",
            "title": "Either Or ✌️",
            "content": "Use `||` (OR) if **at least one** needs to be true.\n\n`true || false` is `true`.",
            "codeSnippet": "let hasTicket = false;\nlet isVip = true;\n\nif (hasTicket || isVip) {\n  console.log('Enter!');\n}",
